metadata.name: Layne the Nihon Warrior (Redeem) Open Edition
metadata.description:
IMPORTANT! Redeem token!

Once this is in your wallet, you can redeem the full comic book in hi res. PDF by going here:  
https://laynetnw.orvylle.xyz/  
and connecting the same wallet. Always use a burner!

Unofficial comic book about G.U. #9761, created by Sygo, OG holder, Lore Core and AV Core Council member of Genuine Undead.

Barely coping with his frenetic life through a near future dystopian Tokyo, in the year 2047, Layne soon will found himself involved in things far bigger than him, and he will be pushed to the edge.

You don't choose G.U., it's G.U. that chooses you.

10% of Mint and 50% of all royalties will go to the Genuine Undead community wallet as a form of respect to the original art and the awesome Community.

Holders of this token will have future benefits for all my upcoming projects
